{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"796","heading":"Registry of disaster response contractors","label":"796 Registry of disaster response contractors","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/ch2/schII/ptD","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","References in TextThe Small Business Act, referred to in subsec. (a)(2), is (1 et seq.), , , which is classified generally to chapter 14A (§ 631 et seq.) of Title 15, Commerce and Trade. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under and Tables.Pub. L. 85–536, § 272 Stat. 384section 631 of Title 15July 18, 1958"],"amendments":["References in TextThe Small Business Act, referred to in subsec. (a)(2), is (1 et seq.), , , which is classified generally to chapter 14A (§ 631 et seq.) of Title 15, Commerce and Trade. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under and Tables.Pub. L. 85–536, § 272 Stat. 384section 631 of Title 15July 18, 1958"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Definitions","label":"a Definitions","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the term “registry” means the registry created under subsection (b); and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the terms “small business concern”, “small business concern owned and controlled by socially and economically disadvantaged individuals”, “small business concern owned and controlled by women”, and “small business concern owned and controlled by service-disabled veterans” have the meanings given those terms under the Small Business Act ( et seq.).15 U.S.C. 631","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Registry","label":"b Registry","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"In general","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Administrator shall establish and maintain a registry of contractors who are willing to perform debris removal, distribution of supplies, reconstruction, and other disaster or emergency relief activities.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Contents","label":"2 Contents","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796%2Fb%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the name of the business concern;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796%2Fb%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the location of the business concern;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/2/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796%2Fb%2F2%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the area served by the business concern;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"D","heading":null,"label":"D","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/2/D","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796%2Fb%2F2%2FD","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the type of good or service provided by the business concern;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"E","heading":null,"label":"E","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/2/E","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796%2Fb%2F2%2FE","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the bonding level of the business concern; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"F","heading":null,"label":"F","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/2/F","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796%2Fb%2F2%2FF","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/2/F/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/2/F","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796%2Fb%2F2%2FF%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a small business concern;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/2/F/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/2/F","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796%2Fb%2F2%2FF%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a small business concern owned and controlled by socially and economically disadvantaged individuals;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"iii","heading":null,"label":"iii","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/2/F/iii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/2/F","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796%2Fb%2F2%2FF%2Fiii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a small business concern owned and controlled by women; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"iv","heading":null,"label":"iv","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/2/F/iv","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/2/F","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796%2Fb%2F2%2FF%2Fiv","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a small business concern owned and controlled by service-disabled veterans.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":"Source of information","label":"3 Source of information","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796%2Fb%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":"Submission","label":"A Submission","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/3/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796%2Fb%2F3%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Information maintained in the registry shall be submitted on a voluntary basis and be kept current by the submitting business concerns.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":"Attestation","label":"B Attestation","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/3/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796%2Fb%2F3%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/3/B/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/3/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796%2Fb%2F3%2FB%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"an attestation that the information is true; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/3/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/3/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796%2Fb%2F3%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"documentation supporting such attestation.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":"Verification","label":"C Verification","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/3/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796%2Fb%2F3%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Administrator shall verify that the documentation submitted by each business concern supports the information submitted by that business concern.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":"Availability of registry","label":"4 Availability of registry","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796%2Fb%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The registry shall be made generally available on the Internet site of the Agency.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":"Consultation of registry","label":"5 Consultation of registry","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s796/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs796%2Fb%2F5","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"As part of the acquisition planning for contracting for debris removal, distribution of supplies in a disaster, reconstruction, and other disaster or emergency relief activities, a Federal agency shall consult the registry.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}
